         MOVE  IX-GYO       TO  WK-SELGYO
     ELSE
         IF  ERR-FLG = ZERO
             MOVE  12       TO  ERR-FLG
         END-IF
         MOVE  "C"          TO  EDIT-CURSOR OF DSP-MSENTA(IX-GYO)
         MOVE  "R"          TO  EDIT-OPTION OF DSP-MSENTA(IX-GYO)
