               PERFORM  PARA-OT-SEC
               CALL "SJR0490I" USING  LINK-JIKKBN
                                      LINK-BUMON
                                      LINK-TANCD
                                      LINK-TOKCD
                                      LINK-TENCD
                                      LINK-KENDT
                                      LINK-DENNO
                                      LINK-CHGKDT
